				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok, I just have to know.
<br />
I've looked into the 3rd party programs, and I've seen one thats pretty interesting. Allowing bards to AE/Chant a hella lot, I read a post about a bard doing it in PoV 18+ hours?
<br />

<br />
Granted thats Overkill, but what are your thoughts on using this for AE'ing/Chanting?
<br />

<br />
I know, &quot;Using these programs will reduce your ability to kite efficently!&quot;, &quot;Macro's are lame!&quot;, &quot;You will be banned if caught!&quot;.
<br />

<br />
I've thought of all these issues, and I know how to kite, AE and Chant..Swarming, well im afraid of Charm have been since my newbie chanter lol
<br />

<br />
I know its morally wrong, and whats the point in playing a bard or any class, or everquest if your just going to let it play the game for you; go back to Single player games wtfz.
<br />

<br />
I could list any numbers of flames to this issue
<br />

<br />
But thats what I want, I want your feedback about Bards and 3rd party macros. Flames, bad notes(pun), good notes(pun).
<br />

<br />
Crazynotez</span></td>
